import Layout from '@/layouts/_layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Blog'>
  <div class='w-full h-uiMinHeight flex flex-col items-center gap-y-10'>
    <h2 class='text-4xl font-bold'>My company blog</h2>
    <div class='w-10/12 h-max rounded-uiRounded py-7 px-8 border-2 border-uiNeutral'>
      <p>
        Welcome to my blog! I am a dedicated developer in the web 3 space, currently working with TaigaLabs, a talented team focused on building
        innovative blockchain solutions. My passion for decentralized technologies drives my commitment to creating products that enhance user
        experiences and revolutionize the way we interact with the digital world.
      </p>

      <p>
        One of our standout projects at TaigaLabs is Dexlot, a cutting-edge decentralized exchange (DEX) designed specifically for delayed order
        trading. Dexlot empowers users to place orders at their desired price points, providing the flexibility to optimize their trading
        strategies without the immediate pressures often associated with traditional platforms. This unique approach allows traders to execute
        trades when market conditions align with their objectives.
      </p>

      <p>
        In my blog, I share insights and experiences related to my journey as a web3 developer and the innovative work being done at TaigaLabs.
        Here’s what you can expect to find:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            In-Depth Tutorials: I’ll cover various aspects of blockchain development, from smart contract creation to integrating decentralized
            applications (DApps). Whether you’re a beginner looking to learn the basics or an experienced developer seeking advanced techniques,
            my tutorials are designed to provide valuable insights and practical knowledge.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            Updates on Dexlot: Stay informed about the latest developments and features of Dexlot. I’ll share updates on new functionalities,
            improvements, and how our team is continually enhancing the user experience. Your feedback is essential, and we aim to create a
            platform that meets the needs of our users.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            Market Analysis and Trading Strategies: As someone deeply involved in trading, I will provide market analysis and share effective
            trading strategies that can help you navigate the ever-changing landscape of cryptocurrency markets. Learn how to leverage delayed
            orders to your advantage and maximize your trading potential.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            Exploration of Web3 Trends: The web3 space is constantly evolving, and I’m committed to exploring the latest trends, technologies,
            and innovations that are shaping the future of decentralized finance (DeFi). I’ll discuss new protocols, tools, and developments that
            can help you stay ahead in this dynamic environment.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            Community Engagement: I believe in the power of community and collaboration. Through my blog, I hope to connect with fellow
            developers, traders, and enthusiasts who share a passion for blockchain technology. I encourage discussions, questions, and sharing
            of ideas, as we all learn and grow together.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
